    </div>

    <div class="prose-shopify card mt-12">
      <h2>TCPA, consent, and cost-per-message discipline</h2>
      <p>Never migrate SMS subscribers without consent timestamp and opt-in source. Email marketing permission does not transfer. Re-verify checkout and popup copy on the new platform before enabling automations.</p>
      <p>Model message fees and discount depth together. A cheaper platform that encourages broadcast blasts can raise opt-outs and destroy list value within one sale season.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="prose-shopify card mt-8">
